WEBVTT

00:02:58.037 --> 00:03:02.026
"Bahor" ning birinchi qismi
bahor kuyi bilan boshlanib,

00:03:02.026 --> 00:03:12.836
huddi shu kuyning ozgina
o'zgargan shakli bilan yakunlanadi.

00:03:12.836 --> 00:03:15.466
Bu -tingolvchi e'tiborini
tortishning to'g'ri yo'li edi,

00:03:15.466 --> 00:03:16.689
va Vivaldi,

00:03:16.689 --> 00:03:20.976
XVIII asr boshining eng zabardast
skripkachilaridan biri,

00:03:20.976 --> 00:03:23.930
ommani jalb etishning qiymatini
yaxshi tushunar edi.

00:03:23.930 --> 00:03:27.639
Bunday konsertlarda u skripka chalish
san'atining yulduzi edi.

00:03:27.639 --> 00:03:30.150
Ba'zida unga "Pieta"ning
talabalari hamroh bo'lgan.